#!/usr/sbin/nft -f
#
# Protection 3: ARP Anti-Spoofing (generated at runtime)
#
# This file is intentionally a documented template. Mininet MAC addresses are
# generated dynamically, so the usable ruleset must be generated after the
# topology starts.
#
# Use:
#   ws2 sh protection/protection_3_apply.sh 10.1.0.1
#   r1  sh protection/protection_3_apply.sh 10.1.0.2
#
# The helper resolves the current legitimate MAC and loads a concrete nftables
# ARP rule that drops forged replies for that IP.
